chunk_content: W CXCA_SCRN Testing Number of women living with HIV on ART screened Semi-Annual X for cervical cancer CXCA_TX Treatment Percentage of cervical cancer screen-positive Semi-Annual women who are living with HIV and on ART eligible for cryotherapy, thermocoagulation or LEEP who received cryotherapy, thermocoagulation or LEEP GEND_GBV Prevention Number of people receiving post-gender-based Semi-Annual violence (GBV) clinical care based on the minimum package HRH_PRE Health Systems Number of new health workers who graduated Annual from a pre-service training institution or program as a result of PEPFAR-supported strengthening efforts, within the reporting period, by select cadre HTS_INDEX Testing Number of individuals who were identified and Quarterly tested using Index testing services and received their results HTS_RECENT Testing Number of newly diagnosed persons living with Quarterly X HIV who received testing for recent infection with a documented result during the reporting period HTS_SELF Testing Number of individual HIV self-test kits distributed Quarterly X HTS_TST Testing Number of individuals who received HIV Testing Quarterly X Services (HTS) and received their test results KP_MAT Prevention Number of people who inject drugs (PWID) on Annual medication-assisted therapy (MAT) for at least 6 months KP_PREV Prevention Number of key populations reached at least once Semi-Annual X with individual and/or small group-level HIV primary or secondary prevention interventions designed for the target population LAB_PTCQI Health Systems Number of PEPFAR-supported laboratory-based Annual X testing and/or Point-of-Care Testing (POCT) sites engaged in continuous quality Improvement (CQI) and proficiency testing (PT) activities.
